Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was raised on an island after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fishing rod...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... um, is your baby okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at six months now. The baby's doing well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Table manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like I'm a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 13, and I should be in seventh grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but stuff happened on the day of the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good! So good! So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's all so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are just emergency rations...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Generation Bleu is overseeing a food supply chain as well, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... You really should ask for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Generati... You mentioned them earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the name of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not a country...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right. This is Earth after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's entirely different from the one I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka, what was your Earth like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of the Scub Coral?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We have it here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's a lot more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It covers the entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People were living on the top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans and the Scub Coral lived together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have authority on this matter, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact the Secretary of Defense directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's back! Eureka! The one that disappeared 10 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention she has a new Mark I,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, a Mark II with her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we won't—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, it's in Japanese waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just let the Japanese take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,Sorry for causing you all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reserve, so I've always been prepared to stand on the frontline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with Japan being as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Generation Bleu is denying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but from our surveillance photographs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly believe my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I asked you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Japanese army, you're the only one who survived the Scub Burst 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you negotiate with Eureka,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could very possibly convince her to cooperate with our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Endo, it's my honor to welcome you on board of my vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good ship, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Nakamura, what exactly is the meaning of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got on board without asking a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously going on a mission with your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped the Nirvash here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that woman for myself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that this ship is just on lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government isn't determined enough yet to face off against Generation Bleu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I thought you liked trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know we reentered the atmosphere as fast as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still weird that a woman came out of the Scub Coral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao hasn't been keeping in contact either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. Here, have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this Eureka person anyway? Everyone acts weird whenever her name is mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Hannah even left space for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a woman beyond common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka is Ao's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard that, but I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know she saved your life ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what we have right now is a mysterious being that emerged along the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware, Mama Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's back... She's back... The birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been since Mama last went down to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this Eureka anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, when a Scub Coral appears, a Secret emerges and a Scub Burst happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the natural order. At least it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ten years ago in Okinawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the first time, mankind fought back against the Secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were taught that Scub Bursts can be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when Generation Bleu was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is the Japanese Navy heading there, the Okinawan Allied Forces are making an appearance too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not too late to command Fukai Ao
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to bring back the woman that looks like Eureka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we would have to abandon that huge ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let Japan or America have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a complete sample is unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao is also on highest alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really a good idea to leave it to a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of dispatching team Goldilocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost that blue haired girl once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when she's going to vanish again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose her due to any hasty actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gekko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's the name of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I traveled on it with many other people a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all on a journey together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Was his father traveling with you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at first it wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were pretty much like children back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a crybaby as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kind of useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did. Every bit of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, and was Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I think Renton will come for me though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't really know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renton?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To research the cause of the disappearing Scub Coral,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we purposely allowed the Scub Coral to consume this ruined ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But while we were conducting the experiment, we were both caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both? The other Nirvash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're piloting a Nirvash too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks just like the one Renton is building now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a call earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my chief and sub-chief. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ivica Tanovic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ivica Tanovic, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr Ivica...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ivica, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've met you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard you fell to Okinawa two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was way before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've came here once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mr. Endou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Monster, closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is impossible! We should leave it to the air force!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the calculations are correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then a Scub Burst here could erase the entire main island of Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to trust that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And believe what she said about that Quartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to take it... with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she has a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We took his mother away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to her, we now know how to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't defeat the Secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can prevent the Scub Burst by retrieving the Quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Christophe Blanc. If you'd like, please join the organization I'm plannin—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must return to my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many sons are close to losing their mothers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I think this is the first time we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Chief, you said you knew Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka from the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't given birth to you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came from a time before she showed up at Iwato island 13 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that... her baby is... me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have managed to link some data to that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I could only identify the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The date of the data is 12005 AD.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that ship is from the distant future?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Eureka isn't an alien? She's from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten thousand years and two thousand more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for jokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the cause of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,And even if all goes well and I give birth to him, wouldn't he just hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0150,,Stop there if you really think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell in love with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're bearing his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you're just starting to worry about the child now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you just focus on how to overcome the difficulties?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the doctors said that inside of areas with high trapar concentration,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the child of a human and a Coralian would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blanc, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gazelle Corps is an independent contractor under direct control of the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, he somehow ended up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. How did you find us in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your mom, Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by the JAF and the Allied Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can use the Triton as a decoy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use the GenBlu transporter, which is standing by, to retreat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mom doesn't want to leave here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll return her to her world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we have her, the research on Scub Coral and Secrets will progress a lot faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fated to come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of a way to return her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't want Generation Bleu to take her—Eureka—away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall for her, ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being retarded, Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always pretending to know it all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get in our way all the freaking time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of gunpowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me—!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is you, Eureka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman who was with you is unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hannah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You're Endo from the ground forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep them cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't while they have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but it can't stay as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's gonna stay with me! I won't let anyone take her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Is that Eureka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, let's escape together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief said he'll send you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the child you're carrying is me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then this way I won't get... born...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow, Eureka's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being so rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this world you can't trust the Allied Forces nor Generation Bleu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Japanese, are the only ones truly wishing for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao... My Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao! Return to where I belong... to Renton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. A terrible thing is about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secrets aren't your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean the Secrets aren't our enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? He protected you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a rude greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step away, Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Ao! You can't change this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... o...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.32,0:22:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years old. A real troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me, please take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to protect her child!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where am I or who those people are, but I only know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I have to protect this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.69,0:23:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nirvash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth and the two Nirvash face off in a wild battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret that appears in the middle of the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cracks the walls of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The revealed truth pulls Ao into despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka Seven AO, episode 14: Starfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.97,0:24:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
